<ul>
    <li><strong>Flavored E-Liquid Bans: A Major Blow:</strong> For many adult vapers, including RELX users who appreciate the variety of flavors, <strong>flavored e-liquid bans</strong> have been a game-changer. These bans, often implemented at the state or local level, directly impact the appeal of vaping for adults seeking alternatives to traditional cigarettes. When popular flavors are removed from shelves, <strong>vaping product sales decrease</strong> drastically, directly impacting vape shop revenue. Imagine a shop that relied heavily on fruit and dessert flavored RELX pods – a ban on these flavors can cripple their business. <a href="https://www.relxvape.co.uk/products/infinity-pod">Discover the best RELX pod flavors</a>.</li>
