<p><strong>4. The Lingering Effects of Past Controversies:</strong></p>

<p>Past health scares and controversies surrounding vaping, even if not directly related to reputable brands like RELX, can cast a shadow over the industry. These events can erode consumer confidence and contribute to a general sense of uncertainty around vaping, impacting <strong>vaping product sales decrease</strong> in physical stores.</p>

